---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="Home">
  <div class="page hero">
    <p class="eyebrow">Founder CTO · AI-First SaaS Architect · Startup CTO</p>
    <h1>Systems builder, currently building AI-first.</h1>
    <p class="lede">
      27+ years of software engineering, architecture, and technology leadership — web,
      enterprise platforms, cloud &amp; integration, and now AI-native SaaS. Currently CPTO at
      ServiceBuddy and building ventures through Stealth (WIP), following CTO roles at
      Cognosic and Leasi.
    </p>
    <p class="motto">Build. Learn. Share. Repeat.</p>

    <div class="entry-points">
      <a class="card" href="/about"><h3>About</h3><p>The through-line, the philosophy, and the values behind the work.</p></a>
      <a class="card" href="/experience"><h3>Experience</h3><p>27 years across four technology eras, from web engineering to AI-native SaaS.</p></a>
      <a class="card" href="/ideas"><h3>Ideas</h3><p>Why AI, why SaaS, why startups, why architecture — the reasoning, not just the résumé.</p></a>
      <a class="card" href="/case-studies"><h3>Case Studies</h3><p>Two concrete builds: migrating Leasi off low-code, and building ServiceBuddy AI-first.</p></a>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
  .hero .lede {
    font-size: 18px;
    color: var(--ink-soft);
    max-width: 62ch;
  }
  .motto {
    font-family: Georgia, "Iowan Old Style", "Palatino Linotype", serif;
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: 20px;
    color: var(--accent);
    margin: 28px 0 40px;
  }
  .entry-points {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 16px;
  }
  @media (max-width: 560px) {
    .entry-points { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  }
</style>
